description: Bridges: Method deleteStorageTimestamps must have `public function delete<DomainEntity>Collection(<DomainEntity>CollectionDeleteCriteriaTransfer): <DomainEntity>CollectionResponseTransfer;` signature. https://spryker.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/CORE/pages/478052552/Application+Namespace+Conventions#ApplicationNamespaceConventions-Facade

Bridges: The bridge interface has incorrect method signature for `deleteStorageTimestamps()`. 0 params expected but got 1. Got `array $timestamps` but expected to be `array $keys`. Missed return type. That violates the rule "All bridge interface methods must have exactly the same or more strict signature as their parent"
